node.text:
Styx romance

I mean being a master of the underworld has its perks, right?
Now that Persephone & Hades are OFFICIALLY a couple, they might as well have some good times!!

And Cerbie can also have a little taste of Venise that way 🐶🐶🐶!

Sorry for the lack of comics this last weeks, holidays with the family got in the way( And I regret nothing 😆 )! You can expect more posts from now on, we're back 🙂 !

#mythology #charon #cerbie #love #romance #relationship #couplegoals #comics #art #webcomics #funny

node.text:
The customer is always right !

Charon joined the Goofy Gods cast, and let's be honest, Charon IS the underworld's only Uber.

I remember the first time I took an Uber, I was reluctant at first (mostly because I didn't want to learn how to use a new app :D) but when i saw that it was faster, cheaper AND you had free candies (in Paris at least), I quickly changed my mind :D

Is it the same in your countries?

#UnderworldUber #igcomics #customerservice #webcomics #Charon #Styx #Greekmythology #Underworld #Obolus #hades #toon #comics

node.text:
Last part of Hades/Persephone story!! Part 12! 

Love always finds a way!

Admitting you are wrong takes a lot of strengh and to to be willing to make things right takes even more so. Luckily Demeter doesn't lack any (you know, being goddess of the harvest, agriculture and all 🙂 )

This was the last part for this "demeter arc" story. I really had a blast drawing it and I hope you enjoyed reading it as well ^^ !

Don't worry though cause we have many more ideas to come which will also include Cerbie Hades and Persephone ( especially now that the last two are OFFICIALLY a couple 😀 ).

#relationship #love #couple #dating #romance #affair #persephone #hades #toon #comics #webcomics #igcomics

node.text:
Hades/Persephone story part 11

Grandmother Gaia and Demeter have a talk. 

Could Hades know something about life after all? Taking care of a puppy is no easy task if you want to do it right.

Not everyone will get why the 5th panel is painful, but those who do get extra love from us cause it probably means you've been following us for more than a year now. Thanks so much for sticking around 😃
For the others, check our story today the explanation will be there ☺️

node.text:
Hades/Persephone story part 10

Hades and Cerbie's perfect plan to date Persephone again is quickly falling appart. It appears there's more to life than playing, eating and sleeping, who would have thought...

Looks like its over guys, I mean, what can they do? Kidnap her to save her? Not sure Demeter would be happy about that...

node.text:
Hades/Persephone story part 9

Some say « mother knows best » but I guess it's not always true. 

Overprotective parents can be pretty harmful, but in a way, I can relate. Even though my daughter is just a baby, I can already tell I'm gonna struggle finding the right balance 😃.
